text:
Wiper boss Kalonzo Musyoka has said Kenyans should ignore anti-vax social media propaganda & get vaccinated against #COVID19.

He said all Kenyans should get the #AstraZeneca Covid-19 #vaccine since vaccination is the only way to stay safe & keep others safe.

Nairobi / Sonko https://t.co/Q1ZwKJGEcF
